    <br>
    <b> Example 3</b>
    <br>
    Find the next 3 terms in 10, 9, 8, 7, 6, ----, ----, ----
    <br>
    <b>Solution</b>
    <br>
    10, 9, 8, 7, 6, <b>5</b>, <b>4</b>, <b>3</b>
    
